==Notes==
*Located northwest of [[Britain]], southeast of [[Yew]], northeast of [[Shame]], and southwest of [[Despise]].
*Receives the 50% Dungeon Skill Gain Bonus.
*You won't be attacked by the orcs here if you are wearing an orc mask
*There are many mushrooms which hurt you when closeby
